column2: select distinct top # astar.ra, astar.dec,  #*(astar.ra - ap.racen)/cos(ap.deccen*PI()/#) as xfocal,  #*(astar.dec - ap.deccen) as yfocal, obj.j as mag from apogeestar as star, apogeeObject as obj, apogeePlate as plate   where     obj.target_id=star.target_id     and plate.location_id=star.location_id     and plate.plate = #     order by mag
